-- Toro Energy's Hall Says Financing for Uranium Projects Lags Behind Demand
-- B y   J a s o n   S c o t t
-- 2010-10-19T04:01:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/toro-energy-s-hall-says-financing-for-uranium-projects-lags-behind-demand.html
Toro Energy Ltd., the uranium
explorer seeking to develop the Lake Way-Centipede deposit in
Western Australia, said financing for projects lags behind
demand for the nuclear fuel.  Toro Energy Managing Director  Greg Hall  made the comments
to a forum in Perth today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Scott in Perth at 
